cs.SY, cs.Optimization, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with solving nonlinear optimal control problems using an iterative algorithm based on linear-quadratic approximation. This is a topic that falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.Optimization). The use of iterative methods and approximation techniques also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of Gaussian noise in the problem formulation suggests a connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
